{"talk":{"id":62628,"name":"Tom Rivett-Carnac: How to shift your mindset and choose your future","description":"When it comes to big life problems, we often stand at a crossroads: either believe we're powerless against great change, or we rise to meet the challenge. In an urgent call to action, political strategist Tom Rivett-Carnac makes the case for adopting a mindset of \"stubborn optimism\" to confront climate change -- or whatever crisis may come our way -- and sustain the action needed to build a regenerative future. As he puts it: \"Stubborn optimism can fill our lives with meaning and purpose.\"","slug":"tom_rivett_carnac_how_to_shift_your_mindset_and_choose_your_future","recorded_at":"2020-04-22 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-04-22 19:54:31","updated_at":"2021-04-13 21:31:23","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":644,"name":"TED2020 "},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/3b373180746c0087823a64d35bee71ef6fea69b7_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/3b373180746c0087823a64d35bee71ef6fea69b7_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/3b373180746c0087823a64d35bee71ef6fea69b7_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/3b373180746c0087823a64d35bee71ef6fea69b7_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/f539f036cd1942ef735411eeb192eecab986f894_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/TomRivettCarnac_2020S-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":7847987,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/TomRivettCarnac_2020S-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":21774059,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/TomRivettCarnac_2020S-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44